      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="25815218">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52492145/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u52492145-9.jpg" alt="Swan" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25815218/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25815218/" class="">第181页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52492145/" class=" " title="Swan">Swan</a>
                (一个娃娃而已....)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25815218">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">借势，就像冲浪高手一样，你要适时站在浪的前面，保持足够的耐心、冷静和体力，并乘机冲上浪巅，而不被大浪所吞没。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-16 20:23</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                借势，就像冲浪高手一样，你要适时站在浪的前面，保持足够的耐心、冷静和体力，并乘机冲上浪巅，而不被大浪所吞没。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

