        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="26230879">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48798037/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48798037-22.jpg" alt="Dylan ﹌" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26230879/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26230879/" class="">2</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48798037/" class=" " title="Dylan ﹌">Dylan ﹌</a>
                (荒岛图书馆in北海善居青年旅舍)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="26230879">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">当下中国的社会结构，原本我们以为它会是一座“金字塔“，但越来越变成一颗”图钉“。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-05-07 19:55</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                当下中国的社会结构，原本我们以为它会是一座“金字塔“，但越来越变成一颗”图钉“。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
